<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> الْحَلِفِ بِعِزَّةِ اللَّهِ وَصِفَاتِهِ وَكَلِمَاتِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">(أَعُوذُ بِعِزَّتِكَ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٦٩٤٨]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَالَ أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(يَبْقَى رَجُلٌ بَيْنَ الْجَنَّةِ وَالنَّارِ،<span class="c5"> فَيَقُولُ:</span> يَا رَبِّ اصْرِفْ وَجْهِي عَنِ النَّارِ، لَا وَعِزَّتِكَ لَا أَسْأَلُكَ غَيْرَهَا)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٦٢٠٤]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَبُو سَعِيدٍ:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">(قَالَ اللَّهُ: لَكَ ذَلِكَ وَعَشَرَةُ أَمْثَالِهِ)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٦٢٠٤]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيُّوبُ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَعِزَّتِكَ لَا غِنَى بِي عَنْ بَرَكَتِكَ)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
